<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="hr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Verificiraj Email</title>
  <style>
    /* ... tvoj postojeći CSS ... */
    
    .resend-section {
      margin-top: 30px;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #eee;
    }
    
    .resend-btn {
      background: #667eea;
      color: white;
      border: none;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 14px;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.3s;
    }
    
    .resend-btn:hover:not(:disabled) {
      background: #5568d3;
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }
    
    .resend-btn:disabled {
      background: #ccc;
      cursor: not-allowed;
      transform: none;
    }
    
    .resend-btn.disabled {
      opacity: 0.6;
    }
    
    #countdown {
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #667eea;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="icon">📧</div>
    <h1>Verificiraj svoj email</h1>
    <p>Poslali smo verification link na <strong><%= userEmail %></strong></p>
    <p>Klikni na link u emailu da verificiraš svoj account.</p>
    
    <div id="status" class="status">
      ⏳ Čekamo potvrdu...
    </div>
    
    <!-- ⭐ Resend section -->
    <div class="resend-section">
      <p>Nisi primio email?</p>
      <button id="resend-btn" class="resend-btn disabled" disabled>
        Pošalji ponovno za <span id="countdown">30</span>s
      </button>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <script src="/verify-email.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
